name: Trece
description:
Trece is an image that depicts that modern spirit of the Inca. Also part from the collection Lights Up - Living Incas.

This collection is centered around a picturesque & sacred town in a Peru. The Inca culture had a unique relationship with rocks and stones: The Incas thought stones were alive and each one had a distinct personality. The streets photographed on a rainy night, portray the celebration of light and darkness, as Incas built these streets with their bare hands. At night, their spirits continue to walk through these streets.
